OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNo 10: MP wrong to conflate
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FMuslims with extremism     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The prime minister believed Lee        
OL,6, Anderson's comments about Sadiq Khan   
OL,7, were unacceptable because they         
OL,8, conflated "all Muslims with Islamist   
OL,9, extremism", Downing Street has said.   
OL,11,FThe former Tory deputy chairman was    
OL,12,Fsuspended from the party after refusing
OL,13,Fto apologise for saying "Islamists" had
OL,14,F"got control" of the London mayor.     
OL,16,FThe PM's official spokesman said the   
OL,17,Flanguage he used was "wrong".          
OL,19,FBut he added that Rishi Sunak did not  
OL,20,Fbelieve Mr Anderson was racist.        
